<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Petition - Stop Phone Ban</title>

<style>
body {
    font-family: Arial;
    text-align: center;
    background-color: #111;
    color: white;
}

.container {
    margin: 50px auto;
    width: 70%;
}

h1 {
    color: red;
    font-size: 40px;
}

.slogan {
    font-size: 22px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

input {
    padding: 10px;
    width: 60%;
    margin: 10px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    border: none;
}

button {
    padding: 12px 25px;
    font-size: 18px;
    background-color: red;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    border-radius: 5px;
}

.warning {
    margin-top: 30px;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: yellow;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<h1>STOP THE PHONE BAN</h1>

<p class="slogan"><b>Teach us, don’t ban us.</b></p>

<p>Phones help us stay connected, access education, and take breaks.</p>

<p class="warning">⚠️ Ignoring technology is pushing the problem away.</p>

<h2>Sign the Petition</h2>

<input type="text" placeholder="Your name"><br>
<input type="email" placeholder="Your email"><br>

<button onclick="alert('Thank you for signing!')">
Sign Petition
</button>

<p style="margin-top:30px;">Share this page with your friends!</p>

</div>

</body>
</html>
